    "MeasurementOdds[op][in] theoretically analyzes the process of measuring \
Pauli string op on the input state in and returns an Association of elements \
of the form value -> {probability, sate}, where value is one of the possible \
measurement outcomes (0 or 1), probability is the probability for value to be \
actually observed, and state is the post-measurement state when value is \
actually observed. MeasurementOdds[Measurement[op]] is equivalent to \
